data.description: Re-introducing this terrific 1,800SF RANCH-STYLE home recently remodeled to includes all these GREAT NEW FEATURES:  NEW WINDOWS (except for one set) ~ TWO (2) COMPLETELY REMODELED BATHROOMS ~  NEW RECESSED LIGHTING ~ ALL NEW VINYL PLANK FLOOR TILE ~ NEW CARPET IN BEDROOMS ~ NEW 2-PANEL DOORS ON THE BEDROOMS ~ NEW CLOSET DOORS ~ NEW REFRIGERATOR, RANGE, MICROWAVE and DISHWASHER ~ NEW TILE BACKSPLASH ~ NEW GARAGE OVERHEAD DOOR ~ NEW COPPER LINES FROM C-BOX TO MAIN WATER LINE ~ plus....a NEW ROOF INSTALLED IN JUNE OF 2022 (5-year transferable warranty). ----- This 3 or 4-BEDROOM, 2-BATH home offers a GREAT LAYOUT that is perfect for daily living and entertaining, and the VERSATILE FLOOR PLAN offers flexible options depending on your Living Space/Bedroom needs.  The L-SHAPED LIVING ROOM / DINING ROOM is quite spacious and boasts a lovely view of the backyard.  Steps away is the KITCHEN which includes a good amount of cabinets and counterspace...set-up a cute bistro table for quick meals on the go!  Just off the Living Room is a HUGE FLEX SPACE (think MASTER BEDROOM or FAMILY ROOM) with an ATTACHED BONUS ROOM that could easily become the ULTIMATE WALK-IN CLOSET or a convenient HOME OFFICE.  The SHARED HALL BATH connects the Flex Room to the living area, and then tucked away down the hall you'll find 3 BEDROOMS each with a good closet and one with an attached 3-PIECE BATHROOM (nice!).  Step outside and see that the BIG BACKYARD is perfect for kids, pets, & gardening!  Rounding out this home is the LAUNDRY / MUDROOM which provides a good buffer between the house and the 1-CAR ATTACHED GARAGE...drop all your bags, coats, and shoes here! ** GREAT LOCATION ~ just minutes away from the expressway, Metra, and local schools, restaurants & shopping. ----- Come see why this house should become your next HOME SWEET HOME, or perhaps your next INVESTMENT PROPERTY!
